@startuml
!define AZURE_COLOR #0078D4
!define SECURITY_COLOR #FF6B6B
!define DEPLOYMENT_COLOR #4ECDC4

title SpektraSystems CloudLabs-Azure - Deployment and Security Sequence Diagram

actor "Lab User" as User
participant "CloudLabs Portal" as Portal
participant "PowerShell\nSetup Scripts" as Scripts
participant "Azure Resource\nManager (ARM)" as ARM
participant "Azure Migrate" as Migrate
participant "Hyper-V\nOn-Premises" as HyperV
participant "Azure VM\n(IaaS)" as VM
participant "Azure Functions\n(PaaS)" as Functions
participant "Cosmos DB" as CosmosDB
participant "Azure Storage\n(Static Web)" as Storage
participant "Azure Monitor" as Monitor
participant "Log Analytics" as LogAnalytics
participant "Application Insights" as AppInsights
participant "Authentication\nService" as Auth

== Lab Environment Deployment ==

User -> Portal: Access CloudLabs Environment
activate Portal
Portal -> Scripts: Trigger setup.ps1
activate Scripts
Scripts -> ARM: Deploy Infrastructure (IaC)
activate ARM
ARM -> ARM: Validate ARM Templates
ARM -> VM: Provision Virtual Networks
activate VM
ARM -> VM: Create Availability Sets
ARM -> VM: Deploy VMs
VM --> ARM: VM Resources Created
deactivate VM
ARM -> Storage: Provision Storage Accounts
activate Storage
Storage --> ARM: Storage Created
deactivate Storage
ARM -> CosmosDB: Create Cosmos DB Instance
activate CosmosDB
CosmosDB --> ARM: Database Provisioned
deactivate CosmosDB
ARM --> Scripts: Deployment Complete
deactivate ARM
Scripts -> Monitor: Configure Monitoring Agents
activate Monitor
Monitor -> LogAnalytics: Create Log Analytics Workspace
activate LogAnalytics
LogAnalytics --> Monitor: Workspace Ready
deactivate LogAnalytics
Monitor --> Scripts: Monitoring Configured
deactivate Monitor
Scripts --> Portal: Lab Environment Ready
deactivate Scripts
Portal --> User: Environment Provisioned
deactivate Portal

== Azure Migrate Deployment Flow ==

User -> Portal: Start Migration Lab
activate Portal
Portal -> Migrate: Create Azure Migrate Project
activate Migrate
Migrate -> Migrate: Initialize Assessment Tools
Migrate -> HyperV: Deploy Migration Appliance
activate HyperV
HyperV -> Migrate: Register Appliance
Migrate -> HyperV: Discover On-Premises VMs
HyperV --> Migrate: VM Inventory Data
Migrate -> Migrate: Assess Migration Readiness
Migrate --> User: Assessment Report
User -> Migrate: Initiate VM Replication
Migrate -> HyperV: Start Replication Process
HyperV --> Migrate: Replication Data Stream
Migrate -> ARM: Prepare Target Azure Resources
activate ARM
ARM -> VM: Create Target VMs
activate VM
VM --> ARM: Target Resources Ready
deactivate VM
ARM --> Migrate: Target Infrastructure Ready
deactivate ARM
User -> Migrate: Execute Test Migration
Migrate -> VM: Deploy Test VMs
activate VM
VM --> Migrate: Test VMs Running
Migrate --> User: Test Migration Validation
User -> Migrate: Confirm Production Migration
Migrate -> VM: Cutover to Production VMs
VM --> Migrate: Migration Complete
deactivate VM
deactivate HyperV
deactivate Migrate
deactivate Portal

== Serverless App Modernization Deployment ==

User -> Portal: Start Modernization Lab
activate Portal
Portal -> Functions: Deploy Azure Functions
activate Functions
Functions -> Auth: Configure Authentication
activate Auth
Auth -> Auth: Setup Identity Provider
Auth --> Functions: Auth Configured
Functions -> CosmosDB: Configure Database Binding
activate CosmosDB
CosmosDB --> Functions: Connection Established
Functions -> AppInsights: Enable Application Monitoring
activate AppInsights
AppInsights --> Functions: Monitoring Active
deactivate AppInsights
Functions --> User: API Endpoints Published
deactivate Functions

User -> Storage: Deploy Blazor Static Website
activate Storage
Storage -> Auth: Apply Authentication Policies
Auth --> Storage: Auth Applied
deactivate Auth
Storage -> Functions: Configure API Integration
activate Functions
Functions --> Storage: API Connected
deactivate Functions
Storage -> ARM: Apply CORS Policies
activate ARM
ARM --> Storage: Security Policies Applied
deactivate ARM
Storage --> User: Website Deployed
deactivate Storage
deactivate Portal

== Security and Monitoring ==

VM -> Monitor: Stream Performance Metrics
activate Monitor
Monitor -> LogAnalytics: Forward Logs
activate LogAnalytics
LogAnalytics -> LogAnalytics: Analyze Security Events
LogAnalytics --> Monitor: Security Alerts
deactivate LogAnalytics
Monitor --> User: Alert Notifications
deactivate Monitor

Functions -> AppInsights: Send Telemetry Data
activate AppInsights
AppInsights -> AppInsights: Detect Anomalies
AppInsights -> Monitor: Forward Insights
activate Monitor
Monitor --> User: Performance Dashboard
deactivate Monitor
AppInsights --> User: Application Health Status
deactivate AppInsights

User -> LogAnalytics: Query Security Logs
activate LogAnalytics
LogAnalytics -> LogAnalytics: Execute KQL Queries
LogAnalytics --> User: Security Audit Report
deactivate LogAnalytics

CosmosDB -> Monitor: Stream Database Metrics
activate Monitor
Monitor -> LogAnalytics: Store Database Logs
activate LogAnalytics
LogAnalytics --> Monitor: Compliance Validation
deactivate LogAnalytics
Monitor --> User: Compliance Dashboard
deactivate Monitor
deactivate CosmosDB

@enduml
